query: SELECT cc.id, cc.reportId, cc.componentName, cc.actualThickness, cc.minimumThickness, cc.mawp, i.vesselTagNumber FROM componentCalculations cc JOIN professionalReports pr ON cc.reportId = pr.id JOIN inspections i ON pr.inspectionId = i.id WHERE i.vesselTagNumber LIKE '%54-11-005%' ORDER BY cc.componentName;
